Comment: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Imprisoned XII
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:44.09,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}nejireta sora wo egaite omou no {ねじれた空を描いて思うの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:44.09,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Peignant mes pensées dans ce ciel torturé
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:51.20,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hane no nai kimi ochireba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:51.20,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Là où toi qui, sans plumes, ne peux que tomber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:58.08,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}furete shimatta shinsei na mono
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:58.08,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,J'ai souillé quelque chose de sacrée
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:06.69,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}konya watashi no shinwa ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:06.69,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Ce soir, tu seras mon mythe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:11.38,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hora nigerarenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:11.38,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Regarde, tu ne peux pas t'échapper
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:17.98,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yowattiku kimi tojikome te
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:17.98,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Je t'ai enfermée, tu es si fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:23.57,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}YOU KNOW I WANT, I WANT, I WANT...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:23.57,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Tu sais, je veux, je veux, je veux...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:28.64,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I WANT YOU SO... I WANT...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:28.64,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Je te veux tellement, je veux...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:32.33,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Inakereba yokatta noni naze
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:32.33,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,J'aurais préféré que tu n'aies jamais été là, pourquoi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:38.53,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}YOU KNOW... YOU KNOW... YOU KNOW... YOU KNOW...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:38.53,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Tu sais... Tu sais... Tu sais... Tu sais...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:42.27,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}YOU KNOW I WANT YOU TO KNOW HOW MUCH I NEED YOU SO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:42.27,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,J'aimerai que tu sâches ô combien j'ai besoin de toi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:46.61,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ima kuruoshii hodo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:46.61,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Et j'en souffre en ce moment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:03.98,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}wakatteru no demo ima wa hisoyaka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:03.98,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,J'ai bien compris, mais maintenant, calmement,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.95,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kimyou na jikan wo tada kimi to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.87,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&H284451&}kimyou na jikan wo tada kimi to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.95,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Je passe ce temps étrange seule avec toi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.87,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H284451&}Je passe ce temps étrange seule avec toi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:17.96,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&H21140F&\c&H6B5541&}tsumetai kono te de aisubeki mono houmuru
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.58,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}tsumetai kono te de aisubeki mono houmuru
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:17.96,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H21140F&\c&H6B5541&}J'enterre de mes mains froides une chose que je devrais chérir
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.59,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,J'enterre de mes mains froides une chose que je devrais chérir
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:24.10,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}watashi wo ukeirete
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:24.10,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Accepte-moi
