Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:30.94,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Sûr le mur de mon cœur
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:37.82,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&H21140F&\c&H6B5541&}shinobu wa rifujin na yume
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:37.82,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H21140F&\c&H6B5541&}se cache un rêve déraisonnable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:41.82,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&H21140F&\c&H6B5541&}I SAY, YOU'RE MINE... YOU'RE MINE...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:41.82,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE7E7E7&\1a&HFF&\3c&H675852&}J'ai dis, tu es miennes... tu es miennes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.44,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&H21140F&\c&H6B5541&}hora sugu soko ni iru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:49.50,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HE7E7E7&\1a&HFF&\3c&H675852&}hora sugu soko ni iru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:49.50,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE7E7E7&\1a&HFF&\3c&H675852&}Tu vois, tu es presque à côté de moi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.07,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HE7E7E7&\1a&HFF&\3c&H675852&}kanawanai soredemo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.48,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kanawanai soredemo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.07,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE7E7E7&\1a&HFF&\3c&H675852&}Ce n'est pas ta place, mais malgré tout...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.48,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Ce n'est pas ta place, mais malgré tout...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:17:02.25,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I WANT... I WANT... I WANT YOU SO, I WANT...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:17:02.25,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Je veux, je veux, Je te veux tellement, je veux...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:05.67,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}omoide nante iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:05.67,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Je ne veux pas de ces souvenirs, alors...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:12.13,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}YOU KNOW... YOU KNOW... YOU KNOW... SO YOU KNOW...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:12.13,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Tu sais... tu sais... tu sais... donc tu sais...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.85,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I WANT YOU TO KNOW HOW MUCH I NEED YOU SO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.85,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,J'aimerai que tu sâches ô combien j'ai besoin de toi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.56,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ima kuruoshii hodo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.56,Imprisoned XII,,0,0,0,,Et j'en souffre en ce moment
